tends Muffles College High School but represented herself, won the platinum medal in the Level 1 computer coding olympiad with her hurricane preparedness project titled Protective Measures.\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2262, \"end\": 2268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belize\", \"score\": 0.9999856315548635, \"rank\": 1.4122311236289746e-05, \"text\": \"Belize\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belize\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belize\"}, {\"begin\": 2278, \"end\": 2284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garcia\", \"score\": 0.9999259671551813, \"rank\": 7.403832618996198e-05, \"text\": \"Garcia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garcia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garcia\"}, {\"begin\": 2298, \"end\": 2313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muffles_Junior_College\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Muffles College\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muffles_Junior_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muffles_Junior_College\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the platinum medal\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"the Level 1 computer coding olympiad\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"her hurricane preparedness project\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"Protective Measures\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Avinda Dhoray, Saiesh Rampersad and Kovid Capildeo from Presentation College, Chaguanas, in Trinidad and Tobago, together won a platinum medal for stellar performance in the Level 2 math olympiad, while a team consisting of Kahlil Phillip, Rochelle Griffith and Tristan Pivotte, former students of TA Marryshow Community College, Grenada, and who are currently on a gap year, earned a platinum medal in the Level 3 math olympiad.\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2504, \"end\": 2513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andre_Rampersad\", \"score\": 0.9999999983197085, \"rank\": 1.0851021527557561e-09, \"text\": \"Rampersad\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andre_Rampersad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andre_Rampersad\"}, {\"begin\": 2538, \"end\": 2569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Presentation_College,_Chaguanas\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Presentation College, Chaguanas\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Presentation_College,_Chaguanas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Presentation_College,_Chaguanas\"}, {\"begin\": 2538, \"end\": 2569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Presentation_College,_Chaguanas\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Presentation College, Chaguanas\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Presentation_College,_Chaguanas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Presentation_College,_Chaguanas\"}, {\"begin\": 2574, \"end\": 2582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinidad_and_Tobago\", \"score\": 0.9999998311318592, \"rank\": 1.6886838264452035e-07, \"text\": \"Trinidad\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinidad_and_Tobago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinidad_and_Tobago\"}, {\"begin\": 2744, \"end\": 2751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan_und_Isolde\", \"score\": 0.9072612340619148, \"rank\": 0.0936340192582094, \"text\": \"Tristan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan_und_Isolde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan_und_Isolde\"}, {\"begin\": 2780, \"end\": 2782, \"title\": \